### Top 20 words
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books/{{bookId}}/vocabulary?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Top 10 starting from offset 50
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books/{{bookId}}/vocabulary?limit=10&offset=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Single word
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books/{{bookId}}/words/elizabeth
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Non-existent word → 404 word_not_found
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books/{{bookId}}/words/qwertyxyz
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Vocabulary before markup ready → 409 markup_not_ready
# Replay this right after upload, before split+markup finish.
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books/{{bookId}}/vocabulary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
